data.description: A GORGEOUS two-story home on a corner lot in a well-established neighborhood makes this home an EASY choice! This home will welcome you with a grand-style entry and ceramic floors. 3 Bedrooms, 2 1/2 Baths, 2 Car Garage. Living/Dining room Combo with a lot of natural light. BEAUTIFUL kitchen with stainless steel appliances. All rooms upstairs have an additional flex space. Over-sized backyard with covered patio & deck, perfect for entertaining family & friends! This Cozy HOME is close to the downtown, City Base, Shopping & Dining. It is conveniently located from Loop 410 & 281. You got to see it!!!   *** OPEN HOUSE *** Sunday, January 28th, from 11-3:00 p.m.
